OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with good sunny spells for
OL,6,FShetland, though some cloud may bubble
OL,7,Fup in the middle of the day. Quite
OL,8,Fcloudy for Orkney but some bright or
OL,9,Fsunny spells breaking out at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry. Sunny and
OL,12,Fthen clear spells for Shetland through
OL,13,Fthe evening and overnight. Largely
OL,14,Fcloudy for Orkney but some clearer
OL,15,Fspells developing at times.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FIt will stay dry with plenty
OL,18,Fof sunshine on Sunday and winds will
OL,19,Fbe light. Somewhat cloudier for Orkney
OL,20,Fat first but good sunny spells soon
OL,21,Fbreaking out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
