OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA dry
OL,6,Ffew days. Plenty of sunshine on
OL,7,FMonday, clouding over for Shetland
OL,8,Flater. Mostly cloudy on Tuesday.
OL,9,FSunnier for Orkney on Wednesday,
OL,10,Fbrighter later for Shetland. Light
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
